content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 790.10 - Establishment of not-for-profit corporations

State Regulations
A not-for-profit corporation seeking Public Health

Council approval to be established as the operator of a hospice shall comply
with the other applicable provisions of this Part and, in addition, shall
furnish the council with a photocopy of its executed proposed corporate
certificate. Notes
